translation.Name: Rula Note - Focus Weapon
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: XE-564 has reached the phase of easily produced prototypes. Multiple prototypes will be manufactured to begin work on the E-564, the model that will be eventually distributed to the French Military.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: XE-564 has been chosen as the preferred model due to its 76% efficiency, when compared to the efficiency of the other models. Hopefully E-564 can be designed and manufactured quickly.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: The energy weapon project that XE-564 and all related models are in has also been renamed to "Focus."
